4 chicken breasts
1 large sweet yellow onion
1lb sliced mushrooms
4oz butter
8oz heavy cream
4oz chardonnay
flour
salt/pepper/garlic to taste
rice

coat chicken sliced into bitesize strip with salt/pepper/garlic flour
cook in melted butter, remove
deglaze pan with wine, cook onions and then mushrooms
add cream and then add chicken back in.

serve over rice
